OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBreezy with band of rain, heavy
OL,6,Fat times, clearing away eastwards by
OL,7,Fearly afternoon. Sunny spells then
OL,8,Fdeveloping, with isolated blustery
OL,9,Fheavy showers. Temperatures near
OL,10,Faverage.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA breezy night with most
OL,13,Fareas remaining dry with longest clear
OL,14,Fspells in the east. Chance of a few
OL,15,Fshowers across the Derbyshire hills.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FSunshine and chance of showers
OL,18,Ffor Sunday, these potentially heavy. A
OL,19,Fwindy day with temperatures mostly
OL,20,Faround average, but overnight ground
OL,21,Ffrost is possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
